metadata.name: Zhurong
metadata.description: You are witnessing the unstoppable power of the Icelandic element of Fire. With the ongoing volcano eruption in Geldingadalir, it is a fresh reminder that Iceland is the center where the four elements of Fire, Earth, Water, and Air are in constant flux and battle for dominance over the land. Collecting all these core elements will unlock the fifth element, the Mysterious Ether.
